{"pageProps":{"post":{"_createdAt":"2022-06-21T14:49:27Z","_id":"acb4f962-5816-4689-bacf-e9eeb569664b","author":{"image":{"_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-339f8e320ddfad52225d31a181b162996e1c02d1-876x876-png","_type":"reference"}},"name":"üëæ Game Master"},"body":[{"_key":"eb9102cfb46b","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"c7abb9bd9f790","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"What is a Smart Contract?"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h1"},{"_key":"2ffaae7b7e29","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"845dd4dd822e0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"As its name ‚Äúsmart‚Äù indicates, a smart contract is a self-executing contract. The agreements between buyers and sellers are directly programmed into codes. The code is in the form of:"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"45ed5245dccb","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"221c4e7e7aa00","_type":"span","marks":["em","strong"],"text":"If"},{"_key":"221c4e7e7aa01","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":" A "},{"_key":"221c4e7e7aa02","_type":"span","marks":["em","strong"],"text":"happens, then"},{"_key":"221c4e7e7aa03","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":" B "},{"_key":"221c4e7e7aa04","_type":"span","marks":["em","strong"],"text":"happens."}],"level":1,"listItem":"bullet","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"f2ff659c5eb0","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"30c0b56d77d90","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The smart contract is usually applied on blockchain and shares the characteristics of transparency and irreversibility."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"2bb401b989fc","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"849b47bf202e0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Through smart contracts, traders can decide their own rules, just like regular contracts that we see every day. The special function of a smart contract is that it will automatically enforce traders to execute the predetermined deals."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"bb83799c3e84","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"f5a3176009a6","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"f5fd2b8aec49","_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-7b8eed5e1249f079c87bc447954bc5ac794f1cc9-1100x550-png","_type":"reference"}},{"_key":"ed9f884665fe","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"45657d06adb70","_type":"span","marks":["em"],"text":"Image source: "},{"_key":"45657d06adb71","_type":"span","marks":["87a93f88586f","em"],"text":"https://www.cysae.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2018.03.08-Smart-Contract-Legal-02-1.png"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"87a93f88586f","_type":"link","href":"https://www.cysae.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/04/2018.03.08-Smart-Contract-Legal-02-1.png"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"212b98b56845","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"11e2f0202c570","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Why Is It Important?"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h1"},{"_key":"3cc644fea0ba","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"5e6d56d33c400","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"Just like other applications of decentralization, the smart contract marks a milestone in the trust system in finance. Trust had always been a problem in the finance world, and many of the worst financial crises are led by the collapse of the trust system. Here, by using a smart contract, technology takes over the role and makes sure the \"game of trading\" is 100% transparent and secure. The principle is simple since humans cannot ensure a 100% justice system, we invented machines and technologies to help supervise the process and increase its reliability."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"c8993a0a8dc5","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"24bf4787635b","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":""}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"f532ec806a48","_type":"image","asset":{"_ref":"image-0da243f385834c3bf1d53fdc4c964bc327f21c82-1600x999-png","_type":"reference"}},{"_key":"8228809087ef","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"4a391aaaba1b0","_type":"span","marks":["em"],"text":"Image source: "},{"_key":"4a391aaaba1b1","_type":"span","marks":["4a43de9586e6","em"],"text":"https://pirimidtech.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/smart-contract-1.png"}],"markDefs":[{"_key":"4a43de9586e6","_type":"link","href":"https://pirimidtech.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/smart-contract-1.png"}],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"102f689fba42","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"ed89333c697b0","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The followings points summarize some key features and importance of the smart contract:"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"ac181c43b92b","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"ffe3209235b70","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Irreversibility:"},{"_key":"ffe3209235b71","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" Once a smart contract is created, it cannot be changed."}],"level":1,"listItem":"number","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"111ea15ef3c2","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"560c4fe9f0c50","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Independence and Decentralized:"},{"_key":"560c4fe9f0c51","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" No third party is involved during the process of agreeing on a contract."}],"level":1,"listItem":"number","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"71f67266049c","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"f75268b2c0c40","_type":"span","marks":["strong"],"text":"Transparency and Security:"},{"_key":"f75268b2c0c41","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":" The smart contracts are encrypted and shared with everyone on the network. Therefore, it is hard for a contract to be hacked or tampered with for personal interest."}],"level":1,"listItem":"number","markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"c929abdbe4d1","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"ede182b51fe40","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"How Does Smart Contract Work?"}],"markDefs":[],"style":"h1"},{"_key":"330637ff9e19","_type":"block","children":[{"_key":"eeef6a4979e20","_type":"span","marks":[],"text":"The following graph summarizes the process of executing a smart contract."}],"markDefs":[],"style":"normal"},{"_key":"913ec35960b3","_typ